organic digital oddities - odo

odo specializes in the development of miniature web games and puzzles - toys - to stimulate the minds of toddlers
create individual libraries of games to train specific areas of thinking depending on the strong side
of your child's character

some of our customers have ordered games for presents as well


The main difference between non-games and traditional video games is the lack of structured goals,
objectives, and challenges. This allows the player a greater degree of self-expression through
freeform play, since they can set up their own goals to achieve.

